    <entry>
      <title>NBA顶级球员得分数据可视化</title>
      <link href="/2025/03/06/4/"/>
      <url>/2025/03/06/4/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>NBA顶级球员得分数据可视化：从小白到大神的进阶之旅</h1><p>在数据可视化的精彩世界里，呈现信息的方式就像NBA球员的球风一样，能决定你是成为&quot;数据乔丹&quot;还是&quot;板凳球员&quot;。今天，我们将通过NBA顶级得分手的数据集，一步步展示如何从&quot;数据小白&quot;进阶到&quot;可视化大神&quot;。我们会用Python中的matplotlib和pandas这两位&quot;全明星球员&quot;，打造两个版本的水平堆叠条形图：一个是&quot;新秀赛季&quot;版本，一个则是&quot;总决赛MVP&quot;级别的专业设计。</p><h2 id="数据准备：球员上场前的热身">数据准备：球员上场前的热身</h2><p>首先，让我们看看今天的&quot;首发阵容&quot;：NBA历史上得分最高的10位球星，包括他们在常规赛和季后赛的得分表现。这些数据就是我们的&quot;raw talent&quot;，等待被我们&quot;教练&quot;的智慧塑造。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> seaborn <span class="keyword">as</span> sns</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">data = [</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;LeBron James&quot;</span>, <span class="number">41837</span>, <span class="number">8162</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Kareem Abdul-Jabbar&quot;</span>, <span class="number">38387</span>, <span class="number">5762</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Karl Malone&quot;</span>, <span class="number">36928</span>, <span class="number">4761</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Kobe Bryant&quot;</span>, <span class="number">33643</span>, <span class="number">5640</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Michael Jordan&quot;</span>, <span class="number">32292</span>, <span class="number">5987</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Dirk Nowitzki&quot;</span>, <span class="number">31560</span>, <span class="number">3663</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Kevin Durant&quot;</span>, <span class="number">30206</span>, <span class="number">4985</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Wilt Chamberlain&quot;</span>, <span class="number">31419</span>, <span class="number">3607</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Shaquille O&#x27;Neal&quot;</span>, <span class="number">28596</span>, <span class="number">5250</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   [<span class="string">&quot;Tim Duncan&quot;</span>, <span class="number">26496</span>, <span class="number">5172</span>]</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将数据转换为单独的列表，便于可视化</span></span><br><span class="line">players = [row[<span class="number">0</span>] <span class="keyword">for</span> row <span class="keyword">in</span> data]</span><br><span class="line">regular_season = [row[<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="keyword">for</span> row <span class="keyword">in</span> data]</span><br><span class="line">playoffs = [row[<span class="number">2</span>] <span class="keyword">for</span> row <span class="keyword">in</span> data]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="版本1：菜鸟赛季的条形图">版本1：菜鸟赛季的条形图</h2><p>先从简单的开始！就像NBA新秀的第一场比赛，这个版本也许不会惊艳全场，但已经具备了基本功。它使用matplotlib的基础&quot;动作&quot;来展示数据。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建DataFrame</span></span><br><span class="line">df = pd.DataFrame(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;Player&#x27;</span>: players,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>: regular_season,</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>: playoffs</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建水平堆叠条形图</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">12</span>, <span class="number">8</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.barh(df[<span class="string">&#x27;Player&#x27;</span>], df[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>], color=<span class="string">&#x27;steelblue&#x27;</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.barh(df[<span class="string">&#x27;Player&#x27;</span>], df[<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>], left=df[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>], color=<span class="string">&#x27;coral&#x27;</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.xlabel(<span class="string">&#x27;Points&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.title(<span class="string">&#x27;NBA Career Points: Regular Season vs Playoffs&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.grid(axis=<span class="string">&#x27;x&#x27;</span>, linestyle=<span class="string">&#x27;--&#x27;</span>, alpha=<span class="number">0.7</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.legend()</span><br><span class="line">plt.tight_layout()</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/top_ten_players1.png" alt="堆叠图"><br>这个版本就像一个能投能传的rookie球员：</p><ul><li>扎实的水平条形图展示每位球员的常规赛得分（基本功）</li><li>堆叠的条形图秀出了季后赛得分（基础配合）</li><li>标题和标签清晰明了（场上沟通）</li><li>网格线帮助读者比较数据（空间感知）</li><li>图例解释了颜色含义（球场意识）</li></ul><p>这种简单的可视化就像是一个ROTY候选人：有潜力，够用，但离全明星还有距离。</p><h2 id="版本2：总冠军级数据可视化">版本2：总冠军级数据可视化</h2><p>现在，让我们打造一个像LeBron James一样全面且强大的可视化！这个版本关注细节，布局精准，颜色搭配专业，就像一个季后赛关键时刻的绝杀球一样令人印象深刻。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建DataFrame（注意数据顺序反转，以便最高分的球员显示在顶部）</span></span><br><span class="line">df = pd.DataFrame(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;Player&#x27;</span>: players[::-<span class="number">1</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>: regular_season[::-<span class="number">1</span>],</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>: playoffs[::-<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fig = plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">12</span>, <span class="number">10</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 关键变化：创建具有特定尺寸的轴以控制位置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 这将在图形中的特定位置创建轴</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># [左, 底, 宽, 高] - 所有值在0-1之间，作为图形的比例</span></span><br><span class="line">ax = fig.add_axes([<span class="number">0.1</span>, <span class="number">0.05</span>, <span class="number">0.9</span>, <span class="number">0.8</span>])  <span class="comment"># 这将图放置在图形的下部</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 绘制条形图</span></span><br><span class="line">y_pos = np.arange(<span class="built_in">len</span>(df))</span><br><span class="line">regular = ax.barh(y_pos, df[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>], color=<span class="string">&#x27;#1e428c&#x27;</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>, height=<span class="number">0.58</span>)</span><br><span class="line">playoffs = ax.barh(y_pos, df[<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>], left=df[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>], color=<span class="string">&#x27;#c60f2d&#x27;</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>, height=<span class="number">0.58</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理外观</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_xticks([])</span><br><span class="line">ax.set_yticks([])</span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;top&#x27;</span>].set_visible(<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>].set_visible(<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;bottom&#x27;</span>].set_visible(<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line">ax.spines[<span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span>].set_visible(<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 计算最大值以保持一致的间距</span></span><br><span class="line">max_value = (df[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>] + df[<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>]).<span class="built_in">max</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加球员姓名和数值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="built_in">len</span>(df)):</span><br><span class="line">   regular_value = df[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>].iloc[i]</span><br><span class="line">   total_value = regular_value + df[<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>].iloc[i]</span><br><span class="line">   player = df[<span class="string">&#x27;Player&#x27;</span>].iloc[i]</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment"># 添加球员姓名</span></span><br><span class="line">   ax.text(<span class="number">0</span>, i+<span class="number">0.25</span>, player, va=<span class="string">&#x27;bottom&#x27;</span>, ha=<span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span>, fontweight=<span class="string">&#x27;bold&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment"># 添加常规赛数值</span></span><br><span class="line">   ax.text(regular_value - max_value*<span class="number">0.01</span>, i, <span class="string">f&#x27;<span class="subst">&#123;regular_value:,&#125;</span>&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        va=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>, ha=<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>, color=<span class="string">&#x27;white&#x27;</span>, fontweight=<span class="string">&#x27;bold&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment"># 添加季后赛数值</span></span><br><span class="line">   playoffs_value = df[<span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>].iloc[i]</span><br><span class="line">   ax.text(regular_value + playoffs_value - max_value*<span class="number">0.01</span>, i, <span class="string">f&#x27;<span class="subst">&#123;playoffs_value:,&#125;</span>&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        va=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>, ha=<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>, color=<span class="string">&#x27;white&#x27;</span>, fontweight=<span class="string">&#x27;bold&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment"># 添加总数值</span></span><br><span class="line">   ax.text(total_value + max_value*<span class="number">0.01</span>, i, <span class="string">f&#x27;<span class="subst">&#123;total_value:,&#125;</span>&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        va=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>, ha=<span class="string">&#x27;left&#x27;</span>, fontweight=<span class="string">&#x27;bold&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_xlim(<span class="number">0</span>, max_value*<span class="number">1.15</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在图形顶部添加主标题</span></span><br><span class="line">fig.suptitle(<span class="string">&#x27;Top Ten Players in Total Points Scored&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">22</span>, y=<span class="number">0.96</span>, fontweight=<span class="string">&#x27;bold&#x27;</span>, fontstyle=<span class="string">&#x27;italic&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在主标题下添加副标题</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.figtext(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.89</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;The players below have the mosts points scored in the NBA History&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">10</span>, ha=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>, fontstyle=<span class="string">&#x27;italic&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在图例前添加额外文字或描述</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.figtext(<span class="number">0.5</span>, <span class="number">0.86</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;See the break down Regular seasons and playoffs&#x27;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">10</span>, ha=<span class="string">&#x27;center&#x27;</span>, fontstyle=<span class="string">&#x27;italic&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在副标题和图之间添加图例</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用bbox_to_anchor定位图例</span></span><br><span class="line">legend = ax.legend(handles=[regular[<span class="number">0</span>], playoffs[<span class="number">0</span>]],</span><br><span class="line">                           labels=[<span class="string">&#x27;Regular Season&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Playoffs&#x27;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">                           loc=<span class="string">&#x27;lower right&#x27;</span>,  <span class="comment"># 位于右下角</span></span><br><span class="line">                           bbox_to_anchor=(<span class="number">0.95</span>, <span class="number">0.2</span>),  <span class="comment"># 微调位置</span></span><br><span class="line">                           ncol=<span class="number">1</span>,  <span class="comment"># 垂直堆叠项目（1列）</span></span><br><span class="line">                           frameon=<span class="literal">False</span>,  <span class="comment"># 图例周围没有边框</span></span><br><span class="line">                           fontsize=<span class="number">15</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                           markerscale=<span class="number">1.5</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.tight_layout()</span><br><span class="line">plt.savefig(<span class="string">&#x27;top_ten_players.png&#x27;</span>, dpi=<span class="number">300</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/top_ten_players.png" alt="堆叠图"></p><p>这个全明星版本包含了一系列&quot;高级得分技巧&quot;：</p><ol><li><p><strong>精确空间控制</strong>：就像詹姆斯的传球视野一样，<code>fig.add_axes</code>让我们能够精准安排图表位置。</p></li><li><p><strong>简约干净设计</strong>：去除所有坐标轴和边框，就像科比的后仰跳投一样干净利落。</p></li><li><p><strong>明确数据标签</strong>：直接在条形上标注数字，让读者像看到篮板数据一样清晰直观。</p></li><li><p><strong>NBA官方配色</strong>：使用NBA风格的蓝色和红色，就像穿上了球队正式球衣。</p></li><li><p><strong>字体层次分明</strong>：不同文本元素有不同字体大小和样式，像球队中不同位置的球员各司其职。</p></li><li><p><strong>高清输出质量</strong>：以300 DPI保存图像，确保你的可视化作品像总决赛转播一样高清。</p></li></ol><h2 id="总结：从板凳到全明星的进阶之路">总结：从板凳到全明星的进阶之路</h2><p>从这两个版本的对比中，我们看到了数据可视化的&quot;选秀到总冠军&quot;的完整进阶之路。版本1就像一个有潜力的新秀，而版本2则是一个成熟的全明星球员，能够在关键时刻交付精彩表现。<br>对于每一位数据&quot;球员&quot;来说，掌握这种从基础到高级的进阶过程至关重要。根据你的&quot;比赛场合&quot;和&quot;对手水平&quot;，你可以选择使用简单直接的版本1快速出手，或者花时间精心策划版本2的完美战术。<br>无论你选择哪种风格，最终目标都是让数据像球场上的明星球员一样闪耀，讲述一个引人入胜的故事。在这个NBA得分榜的例子中，我们不仅看到了谁是历史得分王，还能直观地比较常规赛和季后赛的得分占比，就像看到球员在不同赛场上的表现一样精彩。这正是数据可视化的&quot;总冠军价值&quot;所在！</p>]]></content>
      
      
