      <title>python读取数据与分析</title>
      <link href="/2025/01/18/1/"/>
      <url>/2025/01/18/1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="引言">引言</h2><p>  在计量经济学中，数据的读取与分析是最基本的功夫。Stata虽然强大，但由于其收费，我们可以转而依赖Python。这种开源工具能完成几乎所有数据处理工作，且库高效且易用。<br>  为什么选择Python而不是R？虽然R语言作为统计分析的专业工具，拥有丰富的统计分析包和专为数据分析设计的RStudio界面，但我选择Python作为主要工具，主要基于以下三点考虑：</p><ol><li>Python拥有更庞大的生态系统和活跃的社区支持，这意味着遇到问题时能更快获得解答。从长远来看，Python的应用范围更广，发展前景更加稳定。</li><li>通过Python学习数据分析，不仅能掌握具体的函数应用，还能深入理解编程思维和数据处理的底层逻辑。这种学习体验比单纯记忆R语言函数更有价值。</li><li>目前系统性的Python计量经济学中文教程相对稀缺。通过分享Python数据分析的学习历程，希望能为计量经济学领域贡献一份实用的参考资料。</li><li>话虽这么这么说，遇到我无法解决或者非常麻烦的问题时，我会果断使用R的。</li></ol><h2 id="数据来源">数据来源</h2><p>  数据从各类格式导入，Python都能轻松应对。通过简单的命令，就能把杂乱无章的原始数据转化为可供分析的结构。描述性统计亦然，均值、标准差、分位数等常见统计量可以快速得到，数据的分布、趋势也能通过可视化手段一目了然。在这里，我们用一则从Havarddataverse获取的的真实俄罗斯银行数据（2000-2023）进行演示操作，任何人都可以通过这个链接来下载此数据<a href="https://dataverse.harvard.edu/dataset.xhtml?persistentId=doi:10.7910/DVN/DWUUQJ">data</a>.</p><h2 id="用python读取分析数据">用python读取分析数据</h2><p>  在此示例中，我们使用pandas与openpyxl包来读取xlsx文件。为了优化处理性能并便于演示，我们从数据集中随机抽取1000个样本进行分析（注意使用sample方法时，要考虑数据的时序性？比如，如果数据是按时间排序的，随机抽样可能会打乱时间顺序，影响分析结果。不过本文只是做描述性统计，所以影响不大）。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> openpyxl</span><br><span class="line">dataRaw = pd.read_excel(<span class="string">&quot;financial data of russian banks.xlsx&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">data = dataRaw.sample(n=<span class="number">1000</span>, random_state=<span class="number">42</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(data.head())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  结果显示如下</p><table><thead><tr><th>Bank_Name</th><th>Bank_ID</th><th>Year</th><th>…</th><th>Commission expenses</th><th>Net Other Operating Revenues</th><th>Net Profit or Loss</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>ХОЛМСК</td><td>634</td><td>2003</td><td>…</td><td>26</td><td>648</td><td>5425</td></tr><tr><td>БАНК <a href="http://xn--g0aqf.xn--s0ai">ДОМ.РФ</a></td><td>62</td><td>2005</td><td>…</td><td>40535</td><td>-3438</td><td>72675</td></tr><tr><td>ДОНИНВЕСТ</td><td>173</td><td>2006</td><td>…</td><td>134</td><td>-33221</td><td>9653</td></tr><tr><td>ИНТЕРПРОГРЕССБАНК</td><td>225</td><td>2009</td><td>…</td><td>33213</td><td>-309152</td><td>173041</td></tr><tr><td>КОСМОС</td><td>256</td><td>2021</td><td>…</td><td>5225</td><td>-69313</td><td>4388</td></tr></tbody></table><p>  可以看到数据已经成功导入并且显示出来，接下来我们来查看数据类型与缺失值情况。<br>  通过<code>print(data.info())</code>我们看到这些数据都是非空的（因为有37个变量输出结果比较冗长这里不予以展示）,同时，我们根据倒数第二行输出的<code>dtypes: object(37)</code>注意到这里的37个变量类型均为object。<br>  本文所述案例中,37个变量均被&quot;模糊&quot;地识别为object类型，这种模糊的归类将导致调用describe()方法时仅能获取分类变量的统计特征（如频次、众数），而无法输出连续变量关键指标（如均值、标准差、分位数），严重制约数据的探索性分析。<br>  数据类型误判问题源于Pandas的保守推断策略：当某列存在任意非数值元素时，整列将被归为<code>object</code>类型以规避潜在错误。这种机制虽能保证数据读取的稳定性，但会显著降低后续分析效能。具体而言，错误的数据类型不仅会占用冗余内存（<code>object</code>类型通常比数值类型多消耗50%以上存储空间），更会阻碍统计函数对数值特征的自动识别，使得方差计算、分布检验等基础分析流程失效，进而影响特征工程与建模的准确性。<br>  为了避免这种情况，我们需要明确每个变量的数据类型。如果 Pandas 无法自动识别合适的数据类型，那么我们就需要手动指定，这样才能确保得到更加全面和准确的描述性统计结果。<br>  通过仔细审查原始数据，我们发现该数据集的结构特征明显：仅前三列（<code>Bank_Name</code>、<code>Bank_ID</code>和<code>Year</code>）为字符型数据（注意到这里我们不将<code>Year</code>转化<code>numeric</code>，但是在时间序列分析中，往往需要转化为数值型变量,本文不做时间序列相关分析的展示所以没有必要），而其余列均为数值型变量。基于这一观察，我们可以针对性地进行数据类型转换，以确保后续分析的准确性。让我们进行如下处理：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">numeric_columns = data.columns[<span class="number">3</span>:]</span><br><span class="line">data[numeric_columns] = data[numeric_columns].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors=<span class="string">&#x27;coerce&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> (data.describe(include=<span class="string">&#x27;all&#x27;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  上述代码中，<code>numeric_columns = data.columns[3:]</code>表示选取数据框从第4列开始的所有列（索引从0开始，因此3代表第4列），这些列应为数值型数据。接着，<code>data[numeric_columns] = data[numeric_columns].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce')</code>将这些列转换为数值类型，其中<code>errors='coerce'</code>参数表示在遇到无法转换为数值的元素时，将其转换为<code>NaN</code>（缺失值）而不是报错。最后，<code>describe(include='all')</code>函数会生成包含所有变量（无论是数值型还是分类型）的描述性统计信息，包括计数、均值、标准差、最小值、四分位数和最大值等统计量。</p><table><thead><tr><th>统计量</th><th>Bank_Name</th><th>Bank_ID</th><th>Year</th><th>Commission expenses</th><th>Net Other Operating Revenues</th><th>Net Profit or Loss</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>count</td><td>1000</td><td>1000.0</td><td>1000.0</td><td>1.000000e+03</td><td>1.000000e+03</td><td>1.000000e+03</td></tr><tr><td>unique</td><td>517</td><td>517.0</td><td>24.0</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td></tr><tr><td>top</td><td>РОЯЛ КРЕДИТ БАНК</td><td>484.0</td><td>2007.0</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td></tr><tr><td>freq</td><td>7</td><td>7.0</td><td>58.0</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td></tr><tr><td>mean</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>2.342991e+05</td><td>-1.577184e+06</td><td>8.629342e+05</td></tr><tr><td>std</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>2.940442e+06</td><td>1.629809e+07</td><td>1.235299e+07</td></tr><tr><td>min</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>0.000000e+00</td><td>-3.841784e+08</td><td>-1.151783e+07</td></tr><tr><td>25%</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>6.780000e+02</td><td>-3.272012e+05</td><td>2.870500e+03</td></tr><tr><td>50%</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>4.498500e+03</td><td>-8.038050e+04</td><td>1.700650e+04</td></tr><tr><td>75%</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>NaN</td><td>2.586225e+04</td><td>-5.978500e+03</td><td>8.701650e+04</td></tr></tbody></table><p>  结果显示前三列（<code>Bank_Name</code>、<code>Bank_ID</code>和<code>Year</code>）为分类变量，可以看到它们的唯一值数量（<code>unique</code>）和最高频次（<code>freq</code>）。对于数值型变量，如手续费支出（<code>Commission expenses</code>）、其他营业净收入（<code>Net Other Operating Revenues</code>）和净利润（<code>Net Profit or Loss</code>）等，我们获得了详细的描述性统计信息。接下来的分析就因人而异了。</p><h2 id="简单的可视化">简单的可视化</h2><p>  箱子示数据特征，让我们对这些数据进行简单的可视化分析。数据可视化不仅能帮助我们快速理解数据的分布特征，还能发现潜在的异常值和模式。以下是一个基本的可视化思路，以箱线图为例：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> seaborn <span class="keyword">as</span> sns</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置Seaborn主题和字体</span></span><br><span class="line">sns.set_theme(style=<span class="string">&quot;whitegrid&quot;</span>, </span><br><span class="line">             palette=<span class="string">&quot;pastel&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">             rc=&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;axes.facecolor&#x27;</span>:<span class="string">&#x27;#f7f7f7&#x27;</span>,  <span class="comment"># 设置背景颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="string">&#x27;figure.figsize&#x27;</span>:(<span class="number">12</span>, <span class="number">8</span>)&#125;)    <span class="comment"># 设置画布大小</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 数据预处理部分保持不变</span></span><br><span class="line">dataRaw = pd.read_excel(<span class="string">&quot;financial data of russian banks.xlsx&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">data = dataRaw.sample(n=<span class="number">1000</span>, random_state=<span class="number">42</span>)</span><br><span class="line">numeric_columns = data.columns[<span class="number">3</span>:]</span><br><span class="line">data[numeric_columns] = data[numeric_columns].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors=<span class="string">&#x27;coerce&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">bank_names = [<span class="string">&#x27;1БАНК&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;ЯРИНТЕРБАНК&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">data1 = data[data[<span class="string">&#x27;Bank_Name&#x27;</span>].isin(bank_names)]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将数据转换为长格式（适合seaborn绘图）</span></span><br><span class="line">melted_data = data1.melt(id_vars=[<span class="string">&quot;Bank_Name&quot;</span>], </span><br><span class="line">                        value_vars=numeric_columns,</span><br><span class="line">                        var_name=<span class="string">&quot;Indicator&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                        value_name=<span class="string">&quot;Value&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 过滤掉无效值</span></span><br><span class="line">melted_data = melted_data.dropna(subset=[<span class="string">&quot;Value&quot;</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建箱线图</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">16</span>, <span class="number">10</span>))</span><br><span class="line">ax = sns.boxplot(x=<span class="string">&quot;Indicator&quot;</span>, </span><br><span class="line">                y=<span class="string">&quot;Value&quot;</span>, </span><br><span class="line">                hue=<span class="string">&quot;Bank_Name&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                data=melted_data,</span><br><span class="line">                linewidth=<span class="number">1.5</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                fliersize=<span class="number">3</span>,  <span class="comment"># 异常值点大小</span></span><br><span class="line">                showfliers=<span class="literal">False</span>,  <span class="comment"># 隐藏异常值（数据量大的时候建议开启）     # 添加缺口显示置信区间</span></span><br><span class="line">                width=<span class="number">0.7</span>)       <span class="comment"># 调整箱体宽度</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 美化设置</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.title(<span class="string">&quot;Financial Indicators Distribution Comparison\nBetween 1BANK and YARINTERBANK&quot;</span>, </span><br><span class="line">         fontsize=<span class="number">16</span>, pad=<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.xlabel(<span class="string">&quot;Financial Indicators&quot;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">12</span>, labelpad=<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.ylabel(<span class="string">&quot;Value (Log Scale)&quot;</span>, fontsize=<span class="number">12</span>, labelpad=<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.yscale(<span class="string">&#x27;log&#x27;</span>)  <span class="comment"># 使用对数坐标（根据数据分布可能需要调整）</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 旋转x轴标签</span></span><br><span class="line">ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), </span><br><span class="line">                  rotation=<span class="number">45</span>, </span><br><span class="line">                  ha=<span class="string">&#x27;right&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                  fontsize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加图例美化</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.legend(title=<span class="string">&#x27;Bank Name&#x27;</span>, </span><br><span class="line">          title_fontsize=<span class="number">12</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          fontsize=<span class="number">11</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          loc=<span class="string">&#x27;upper right&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          frameon=<span class="literal">True</span>,</span><br><span class="line">          shadow=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 调整布局</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.tight_layout()</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  我们首先设置了图表的整体样式（包括主题、调色板和画布大小），然后对数据进行预处理并转换为长格式以适应seaborn绘图需求，最后通过boxplot函数绘制箱线图。为了提高可读性，代码中设置了对数坐标轴、旋转了x轴标签，并美化了图例和标题。需要注意的是，当数据量较大时，建议将showfliers参数设为False以隐藏异常值点，使图表更加清晰：结果图呈现如下：<br><img src="/images/boxplot1.png" alt="箱线图"></p>]]></content>
      
      
